Create a continent column for a dataset with a countryCode column

Source: R/get_continents.R
get_continents.Rd

Create a continent column for a dataset with a countryCode column

Usage

get_continents(data, country = "countryCode", original = "iso3c")

Arguments

data

dataset with observations

country

column name of column with country codes

original

type of data in the source column which contains cuntries to identify continent from

Value

dataset of same type that was passed to it. One column of continents.

Examples

get_continents(obsData)
